    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Microsoft Azure is a cloud platform integrated with Microsoft 365 and Entra ID (Azure AD). Enterprise agent deployments often use Azure Container Apps or AKS, Azure Database for PostgreSQL, Azure Cache for Redis, Blob Storage, Key Vault, and Azure OpenAI Service for GPT models inside corporate boundaries."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "What it is"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Azure uses "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "resource groups",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "code"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " to hold related services in a "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "subscription",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "code"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ". "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Azure RBAC",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "code"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " assigns roles at subscription, resource group, or resource scope. Regions map globally like other clouds; Azure OpenAI provides OpenAI-compatible APIs in allowed regions."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Why it matters"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Organizations on Microsoft stack deploy internal copilots and agents with Entra ID SSO, conditional access, and private Azure OpenAI endpoints — meeting data residency and compliance requirements without sending prompts to public consumer APIs."
          }
        ]
      },
