            "type": "text",
            "text": "Enterprise copilot: users authenticate via Entra ID to React UI; API on Container Apps calls Azure OpenAI with content filtering enabled. Tool calls hit internal APIs over private VNet. Postgres stores audit; Blob retains 90-day traces. Conditional Access blocks external identities from admin agent routes."
          }
